fr.apteryx.imageio.dicom
Interface ReceivedObjectListener

public interface ReceivedObjectListener

Interface for use by the Storage SCP when in asynchronous listening mode, that allows more control over the store response sent back to the SCU than StorageSCPListener.

See Also:
StorageSCP

Method Detail

objectReceived

boolean objectReceived(ReceivedObject o,
                       DataSet response)
Called when an object is received. response is a set of data elements that will be sent in the response message when this method returns. It contains the Tag.status element and may be changed in objectReceived.

If this method returns false, the association is aborted without sending any response.
